Package exercise2

This package includes one skeletal implementation class AbstractShape, five Interfaces ICircle, ILine, IRectangle, IShape, ITwoDimensional. It also contains three subclasses Circle, Line, Rectangle that inherit from the AbstractShape class and one Main class Main.
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ICircle  
    ILine
    An Interface that extends IShape.
    IRectangle
    An Interface that extends the following two Interfaces: ITwoDimensional, IShape.
    IShape  
    ITwoDimensional

    Circle

    Line
    A subclass of AbstractShape class.
    Main
    This class implements instances-objects of other classes (Composition) and test their functionality.
    Rectangle
    A subclass of AbstractShape class.
